metadata.name: Peak of Technology #1
metadata.description: Peak of Technology is an NFT collection consisting of 10,000 generative unique robots. Peak of Technology tells the story of the future. A future of 10,000 friendly robots, whose desire is to be available for any human needs. It is now your chance to get hold of one or even more of these unique robots. Each PEAK OF TECHNOLOGY holder has access to a monthly raffle in which one community selected NFT is raffled off. Welcome to the Peak. We will get way beyond. www.peakoftechnologynft.com
